Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California Coast!

Name: The Brickyard
Description: A great rocklimbing spot in the Santa Barbara Mountains, with lots of fun boulder climbs and beautiful views of the SB area

Name: Refugio State Beach
Description: A beautiful beach with a fun, consistent right point break to surf. Note: $10 dollars to park in the park, but you can park for free and walk about 5 minutes in if you stay right after exiting the 101.

Name: Goleta Skate Park
Description: A small Skatepark in Goleta newly opened this year (2019)

Name: Alpha Thrift Store
Description: A great thrift store with tons of clothes, dishes, furniture and anything else you might need.

Name: Cajun Kitchen
Description: A delicious restaurant offering breakfast, brunch, and lunch with a Cajun Twist.
